          <p class="vads-u-display--inline-block vads-u-font-size--h3 vads-u-margin--0 vads-u-color--black">
            Help users to&hellip;
          </p>
          
          <h1 id="Stay informed of their form submission status">Stay informed of their form submission status</h1>
            
            
              




<a class="site-component-status__link" href="/about/maturity-scale#use-with-caution-candidate">
  <span class="usa-label site-component-status site-component-status--use-with-caution-candidate">
    Use with caution: Candidate
  </span>
</a>
            
            
          <div class="va-introtext" markdown="1">
            Follow this pattern to notify people when their online form submission is in progress, when we receive their submitted form, and when a system error has caused the submission to fail. These are required notification touch points.
          </div>
            
            








<nav aria-labelledby="component-resources" class="site-component-resources-links">
